   <div class="section" id="section2">
      <div class="section2Inner flexParent">
         <div class="col-sm-9 objectiveContainer">
            <h1>About the Fresno County Peace Officers Memorial Foundation</h1>
            <hr>
            <i class="material-icons editBtn editBtnAboutUs">edit</i>
            <div data-bind="html: aboutUs" id="aboutUs"></div>
         </div>
         <div class="col-sm-3">
            <div class="objectiveContainer">
               <h3>OUR OBJECTIVES & PURPOSES</h3>
               <hr>
               <p>The Fresno County Peace Officers Memorial Foundation, Inc. is organized and its assets are to be used to continue recognizing and honoring fallen peace officers who have died in the line of duty while serving in Fresno County.</p>
               <p>The assets of the Fresno County Peace Officers Memorial Foundation, Inc. will be utilized to construct, maintain, and enhance the Fresno County Peace Officers Memorial in Fresno County Courthouse Park and to administer the annual ceremony conducted during the National Police Week. The Board of Directors may provide for additional assistance, as deemed appropriate, for the families of those officers who are honored.</p>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div><!--board-->
   <div class="section" id="section3">
      <h1>Fresno County Peace Officers Memorial Foundation Board</h1>
      <div class="flexParent">
         <div class="col-sm-6 objectiveContainer">
            <h3>Executive Board Members</h3>
            <hr>
            <h3></h3>
            <div data-bind="foreach: $root.boardMembers">
               <!--this section is only for the Executive Board Members-->
               <div class="col-sm-12" data-bind="css: key">
                  <div class="emailLink">
                     <i class="material-icons">email</i>
                     <div class="popover" data-bind="html: data.memberEmailHTML + '&lt;br/&gt;Click to dismiss.'"></div>
                  </div>
                  <p class="memberTitle"><span data-bind="text: data.memberTitle"></span> | <span data-bind="text: data.memberName"></span></p>
               </div>
               <div class="col-sm-12">
                  <p data-bind="html: data.memberPosition"></p>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div><!--board of directors-->
         <div class="col-sm-6 objectiveContainer">
            <h3>Board of Directors</h3>
            <hr>
            <h3></h3>
            <div data-bind="foreach: $root.boardDirectors">
               <div class="col-sm-12" style="padding-bottom:10px;">
                  <div class="emailLink">
                     <div class="popover" data-bind="html: data.memberEmailHTML + '&lt;br/&gt;Click to dismiss.'"></div><i class="material-icons">email</i>
                  </div>
                  <p class="memberTitle" data-bind="text: data.memberName"></p><!--this section is for the board of directors, NOT executive board members-->
                  <p data-bind="html: data.memberPosition" style="display: inline"></p>
               </div>
            </div>
         </div>
      </div>
      <p>Click the envelope next to a board member's name to send them an email. To hide the email pop-up, click the envelope again.</p>
   </div><!--fallen-->
   <div class="section" id="section4">
      <h1>Fresno County's Fallen Officers</h1>
      <div style="margin: 20px;">
         <p>The Fresno County Peace Officers Memorial Foundation, Inc. is organized and its assets are to be used to continue recognizing and honoring fallen peace officers who have died in the line of duty while serving in Fresno County.</p>
         <p>This website is dedicated to those law enforcement officers who paid the ultimate price.</p>
         <p><strong>Scroll to the right to view more officers.</strong></p>
         <div class="timeline" data-bind="foreach: $root.officers()">
            <div class="item" data-bind="attr:{id: data.officerNumber}">
               <h2><span data-bind="text: data.officerName"></span><br>
               <span data-bind="text: data.date"></span></h2>
               <div class="officerImg" data-bind="style: {backgroundImage: 'url(' + data.officerImg + ')'}"></div>
               <div class="officerBio" data-bind="html: data.description"></div>
            </div>
         </div>
         <div class="modal2">
            <div class="modalInner"></div>
         </div>
      </div>
   </div><!--gallery-->
   <div class="section" id="section5">
      <div class="modal">
         <div class="col-sm-6 modalTitle"></div>
         <div class="col-sm-4">
            <span class="showPC">Choose a photo album:</span> <select class="albumDropdown showPC" data-bind="options: $root.albums(), optionsText: 'albumTitle', value: selectedAlbum, optionsCaption: 'Choose an album...'">
